==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: bùjīng yíshì, bù zhăng yí zhì
===Proverb===
'''[[不经]][[一事]]，[[不]][[长]][[一]][[智]]'''
# You can't know about something unless you experience it; wisdom comes from experience.
===Alternate forms===
[[不經一事，不長一智]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])
